data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath brick home built in the late1970's. With an open living area, updated kitchen and bathrooms, and a large primary suite, this residence offers both comfort and style. Inside, the open living area allows for seamless entertaining and quality family time. The updated kitchen features sleek countertops, a large bar/island with seating area, and ample cabinet space. Both bathrooms have been updated and provide enough space for the whole family with an additional half bath in the laundry room! The spacious primary suite provides a peaceful retreat, while the en-suite bathroom offers luxurious amenities including a large, tile walk in shower. Outside, the fenced backyard on the large, shaded lot is perfect for outdoor activities. Mature trees provide ample shade for hot summer days. Conveniently located in a desirable neighborhood, this home offers easy access to schools, shopping centers, and parks. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful brick home yours. Schedule a showing today and embrace the joys of homeownership.
